quran[8]{c,v,t,f}:
  29,31,"Nígbà tí àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ Wa sì mú ìró ìdùnnú dé bá (Ànábì) ’Ibrọ̄hīm, wọ́n sọ pé: “Dájúdájú àwa máa pa àwọn ará ìlú yìí run. Dájúdájú àwọn ará ìlú náà jẹ́ alábòsí.”",""
  29,32,"Ó sọ pé: “Dájúdájú (Ànábì) Lūt wà níbẹ̀! Wọ́n sọ pé: “Àwa nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa àwọn tó wà níbẹ̀. Dájúdájú àwa yóò la òun àti àwọn ará ilé rẹ̀ àfi ìyàwó rẹ̀ tí ó máa wà nínú àwọn tó máa ṣẹ́kù lẹ́yìn sínú ìparun.”",""
  29,33,"Nígbà tí àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ Wa dé ọ̀dọ̀ (Ànábì) Lūt, ó banújẹ́ nítorí wọn. Agbára rẹ̀ kò sì ká ọ̀rọ̀ wọn mọ́. Wọ́n sì sọ fún un pé: “Má bẹ̀rù, má sì ṣe banújẹ́. Dájúdájú a máa la ìwọ àti àwọn ará ilé rẹ àfi ìyàwó rẹ tí ó máa wà nínú àwọn olùṣẹ́kù-lẹ́yìn sínú ìparun.”",""
  29,34,"Dájúdájú a máa sọ ìyà kan kalẹ̀ lé àwọn ará ìlú yìí lórí láti inú sánmọ̀ nítorí pé, wọ́n jẹ́ òbìlẹ̀jẹ́.",""
  29,35,"Dájúdájú A ti fi àmì kan tó fojú hàn lélẹ̀ nínú rẹ̀ fún ìjọ tó ní làákàyè.",""
  29,36,"A tún ránṣẹ́ sí ará ìlú Mọdyan. (A rán) arákùnrin wọn, (Ànábì) Ṣu‘aeb (níṣẹ́ sí wọn). Ó sì sọ pé: “Ẹ̀yin ìjọ mi, ẹ jọ́sìn fún Allāhu. Ẹ retí Ọjọ́ Ìkẹ́yìn, kí ẹ sì má ṣèbàjẹ́ sórí ilẹ̀.”",""
  29,37,"Wọ́n pè é ní òpùrọ́. Nítorí náà, ohùn igbe líle tó mi ilẹ̀ tìtì gbá wọn mú. Wọ́n sì di ẹni tó dà lulẹ̀, tí wọ́n ti dòkú sínú ìlú wọn.",""
  29,38,"(A tún ránṣẹ́ sí àwọn) ará ‘Ād àti ará Thamūd. (Ìparun wọn) sì kúkú ti fojú hàn kedere si yín nínú àwọn ibùgbé wọn. aṣ-Ṣaetọ̄n ṣe àwọn iṣẹ́ wọn ní ọ̀ṣọ́ fún wọn. Ó sì ṣẹ́rí wọn kúrò nínú ẹ̀sìn (Allāhu). Wọ́n sì jẹ́ olùríran (nípa ọ̀rọ̀ ayé).",""
